---
title: Turkish-Style Beef Flatbreads with Chopped Salad and Tzatziki
description: Taking some cues from the traditional Turkish 'Pide', may we present to you our Turkish Flatbread! This dish is a cousin of the pizza that we all know and love, but with a few twists! The delicious spiced lamb filling is baked in our delightfully flaky puff pastry, served with a refreshing chopped salad and the yogurty, fan-favourite dipper: tzatziki! Happy eating!
